{"tid":720792,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"德漢午餐內摻汞 疑18年毒死21同事","createTime":"2018-06-28T07:58:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-28T15:16:02.000Z","uid":75969,"like":177,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"419982005ddb45e8537ee5021d71bb0629543fb3","tid":720792,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T07:58:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180628/_2018062815414244759.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180628%2F_2018062815414244759.jpg&h=c11db1d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">設計圖片</span><br />\n<br />\n德國一間金屬製造商「ARI Armaturen」的一名56歲的員工，在同事的午餐內放入汞、鉛等金屬元素，並導致一名同事死亡。警方調查後發現，<span style=\"color: red;\">下毒員工疑在18年來已害死21名員工。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n外國傳媒報道，德國西北部的Schlo&szlig; Holte-Stukenbrock小鎮一間千人企業，一名56歲員工犯下連環毒殺案，該男在今年5月被同事發現，午餐麵包被灑上可疑粉末，隨後公司在閉路電視片段發現一名員工偷偷向同事下毒。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，該公司最近至少傳出2宗員工重病案例和重金屬中毒有關，甚至有員工已昏迷2年，過去18年來一共有21名員工死於心臟衰竭或癌症，這些死者可能均因重金屬中毒致死。<br />\n警方已前往該名員工家中搜索，後來發現汞、鉛、鎘等有毒化學物品。目前相關單位正在調查死者的死因是否與重金屬物質有關。<br />\n<br />\nARI Armaturen經理Tilo Blechinger表示，原本他們以為這是同事間的惡作劇，沒想過有謀殺企圖。他指疑犯已在公司工作38年，平時並不顯眼。疑犯被捕後選擇保持緘默。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/752596\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F752596&d=F9d%2FgIgD8apEe27ZTW%2FZcNr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=8b2ffb7d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F752596&h=b317322b\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/752596</a>"},{"pid":"c5b4584d673b5054fee886325d578ab8ea780402","tid":720792,"uid":190928,"like":271,"dislike":4,"score":267,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T08:02:59.000Z","msg":"德國科技世界第一，殺人都可以殺得咁科學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\"